-16T05:42:17.000Z","msg":"又寫鱔稿揾人接貨<br />\n我覺得香港跟本要規管下呢d 收錢寫嘅稿<br />\n一d 要寫明廣告"},{"pid":"85fedd4281082a902757f4bac6b8417892ad1b32","tid":500721,"uid":29625,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:43:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母閪 同蝗蟲有咩分別"},{"pid":"54d7a805895aaf86addf37829303457d4d26b479","tid":500721,"uid":17859,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:45:20.000Z","msg":"賤種港畜"},{"pid":"53a33cb8f5c9eca45c9984c923f92a0fc870d71b","tid":500721,"uid":3464,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:47:52.000Z","msg":"一邊話香港買唔起 （原因支那種炒貴晒）<br />\n一邊去外國炒人地既樓<br />\n同支那人有咩分別 依條女非常垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c61c48ae6480f70aedf5db30720015123d177285","tid":500721,"uid":78546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢地以為日本係香港,俾佢地為所欲為.好快日本見港蝗咁謀利法,就會禁外來人買樓或者圖利.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本人好重視本地人利益，當佢發現影響到自己人就會出招打擊</blockquote><br />\n個邊經濟都唔掂<br />\n冇人接火棒 佢d樓本身都冇人買"},{"pid":"f24fb2454b76cd1b0dbc4ed1cf1c50bac1f79408","tid":500721,"uid":83303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:00:27.000Z","msg":"日本airbnb唔係犯法嫁咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2155a334dbc6f3bacb19cedf87f4d72fa4a6f565","tid":500721,"uid":147467,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:02:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本airbnb唔係犯法嫁咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔比人拉到就唔犯法架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485f625d6180125c5ba700f95b9a6e04a77165fe","tid":500721,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:05:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日本airbnb唔係犯法嫁咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔比人拉到就唔犯法架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對於Airbnb，日本議會早前通過《住宅住宿事業法》，訂出讓房東每年可以將房屋轉租最多180天，法案預計明年第一季推出，令Airbnb正式合法化。大阪市政府並在上月向民宿認證業者發出標誌貼紙，與「地下民宿」區別，另設補助金制度，助民宿經營者完善消防設備的補貼。"},{"pid":"dbb050649a2f7cc1395b590581349466a43a1a44","tid":500721,"uid":92166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:05:42.000Z","msg":"香港人日日聲大大屌鳩強國蝗過黎炒爆哂d樓，自己又去另一個地方做炒樓蝗，講到尾，強國人d炒功炒癮都係師承香港架咋"},{"pid":"37958f67797781d7281c526d258ac4d06bb77d30","tid":500721,"uid":76470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:06:53.000Z","msg":"自己都受緊比人炒貴晒啲樓嘅苦<br />\n而家又去炒貴返人地啲樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2aaa92b1fc2d7578cd01def30fd88ebfc8d186d","tid":500721,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:09:56.000Z","msg":"正仆街"},{"pid":"493a9159075b16915af15e7a530d0d7cd1673574","tid":500721,"uid":45368,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:10:55.000Z","msg":"遲早全世界都唔歡迎香港人<br />\n去到邊炒到邊<br />\n同蝗無撚分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f785360ba7c07c57d7156be95f7b38e7da729fcc","tid":500721,"uid":71676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:13:00.000Z","msg":"遲早比人種族清洗架啦"},{"pid":"b03451d83baad6a2cec05b0b74118b32a56d3d2c","tid":500721,"uid":33439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:15:27.000Z","msg":"日本買樓交稅都交撚死"},{"pid":"4bc7391afe3db87d23d22887a5e666cff5ec038b","tid":500721,"uid":