-12-16T07:24:04.000Z","msg":"香港媒體，除左炒之外，仲識歌頌d乜"},{"pid":"c2adf9ed0de5e57ba9b584b3adee6d66ad8a80bd","tid":500721,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:39:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本舊樓會賺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢都係賺番香港人咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7acc8780d696b45debb6d0594c752ab0cdb4b739","tid":500721,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:46:46.000Z","msg":"唔女"},{"pid":"f8110432c844c9b96079f57320e67d5f7bf6bba3","tid":500721,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔女</blockquote><br />\n唔好理人點講，自己做好功課再出發"},{"pid":"d00e85141f1610b72403536bb8abbf4a0c9898ca","tid":500721,"uid":6931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:52:48.000Z","msg":"咪撚搞人地啲地方啦 正臭閪"},{"pid":"0c5b9312ef4c064bc3cadbf1ddb0c6752a4f7135","tid":500721,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:54:09.000Z","msg":"搞腥簡人好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314f49428fde6a562487090d2547ebb88fe86de4","tid":500721,"uid":59961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:54:18.000Z","msg":"騷擾埋人地既地方 同支那蝗有咩分別"},{"pid":"091643312805cdc3ed47671762f87c54540901e2","tid":500721,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:56:27.000Z","msg":"香港人屌鳩蝗炒貴香港樓價，轉個頭就去炒人哋既樓價<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34cd993b6288be4222718615e590bc99a578cad4","tid":500721,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:16:33.000Z","msg":"其實東京大阪專登起楝樓專做airbnb,  單位賣俾港人做airbnb,， 再請team人做清潔。 半年就留番俾自己同朋友住， 反正大把港人當日本係鄉下"},{"pid":"9f86321ce1043dc590dab1aadcb525b93ea09233","tid":500721,"uid":83226,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:18:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母閪 同蝗蟲有咩分別</blockquote><br />\n其實一開始，香港人都已經係咁，去日本炒，加拿大炒，係近年俾人炒返轉頭就鬧蝗蟲<br />\n<br />\n香港人好清高咩<br />\n其實真係有好多都好仆街<br />\n大陸人係質素低<br />\n但有唔小香港人係聰明但人格低"},{"pid":"4688af663910a5f2de183e0bd145b88d633a4dcc","tid":500721,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:37:34.000Z","msg":"開心幾個月之後食花生等收皮"},{"pid":"a7d9bd1c04633054ea0b4294c241e166a87f9a15","tid":500721,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T11:02:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母閪 同蝗蟲有咩分別</blockquote><br />\n其實一開始，香港人都已經係咁，去日本炒，加拿大炒，係近年俾人炒返轉頭就鬧蝗蟲<br />\n<br />\n香港人好清高咩<br />\n其實真係有好多都好仆街<br />\n大陸人係質素低<br />\n但有唔小香港人係聰明但人格低</blockquote><br />\n論炒樓<br />\n點都係香港人先過大陸"},{"pid":"6f55e845368a9750c59c5cd92df55ae28e45aabb","tid":500721,"uid":27438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T11:30:29.000Z","msg":"強國人恨貪官，恨自己唔係<br />\n香港人恨炒樓，恨自己冇份<br />\n一鳩樣"},{"pid":"eca9485fd78cf42b612d54375a7d6e7fcaad7d4e","tid":500721,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T16:35:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>日本airbnb唔係犯法嫁咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔比人拉到就唔犯法架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對於Airbnb，日本議會早前通過《住宅住宿事業法》，訂出讓房東每年可以將房屋轉租最多180天，法案預計明年第一季推出，令Airbnb正式合法化。大阪市政府並在上月向民宿認證業者發出標誌貼紙，與「地下民宿」區別，另設補助金制度，助民宿經營者完善消防設備的補貼。</blockquote><br />\n得半年bnb 要回本就要加價<br />\n咁點解我唔住酒店</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家唔知佢點計180日<br />\n但我幾肯定依定放係airbnb全部都過<br />\n同埋大阪少酒店 租到都起碼千幾二千晚<br />\n只要平少少真係好多人仆去民宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4738af0267a2be0830a03fae85c54babf442da","tid":500721,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T17:38:47.000Z","msg":"日本D 樓值錢咩，遠少少都求人租咁制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}